xdi2.messaging.container.interceptor

Interface MessageEnvelopeInterceptor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Extension<MessagingContainer>, Interceptor<MessagingContainer>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMessageEnvelopeInterceptor, DeferResultInterceptor, ExecuteCommandInterceptor, ManipulatingInterceptor, SkipLinkContractsInterceptor, VariablesInterceptor, WriteListenerInterceptor

    public interface MessageEnvelopeInterceptor
extends Interceptor<MessagingContainer>
    Interceptor that is executed before and after a message envelope is executed, as well as when an exception occurs while executing the message envelope.
    Author:
    markus
